history.content: Yes you'll have to schedule an appointment with your ESS advisor, and only s/he can provide you the green form. Note that this drop can only be done once in your academic career, and you'll need to be taking at least 8 technical units (+ they need to count for technical requirements for your major) excluding the course to be dropped.
